<p>Key issues:</p>

<ul>
  <li>How the relationship between the artist and the machine has changed artistic expression?</li>
  <li>How machines can become a new kind of medium?</li>
  <li>Can machines enhance aesthetic awareness?</li>
</ul>

<p>During a workshop at Centro Nacional de las Artes, Jos√© Manuel Ruiz invited us to reflect on these questions by exploring the concept of media, theoretically and experimentally by developing an artwork with the machines at the media lab.</p>

