<p>After playing with the photocopier I realized I could use it as a medium for expressing the ‚Äútransduction of the primitive‚Äù. A human process of symbollic exploration that began with the first handprint in a cave, and continued through time with the use of technology: automatic reproduction, replication and transformation of symbols. Below are the results.</p>

